CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776694271
OL,3,CFarage appears to row back on re-
OL,4,Copening Port Talbot's blast furnaces
OL,6,FHowever on a previous visit to Port
OL,7,FTalbot in June 2025 Mr Farage had said
OL,8,Fhe wanted Wales to "re-industrialise
OL,9,Fto prosper and grow" and that could be
OL,10,Fachieved by opening former coal mine
OL,11,Fsites in Wales to provide fuel for
OL,12,FPort Talbot's blast furnaces.
OL,14,FMr Farage added that reopening the
OL,15,Fblast furnaces would cost "in the low
OL,16,Fbillions".
OL,26,@wD@[OU
