SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776694271
OL,3,CFarage appears to row back on re-
OL,4,Copening Port Talbot's blast furnaces
OL,6,FDuring his visit to Merthyr Tydfil, Mr
OL,7,FFarage said it was a two-horse race
OL,8,Ffor the Senedd Election between his
OL,9,Fparty and Plaid Cymru.
OL,11,F"I want us to win, and we aim to win,"
OL,12,Fhe added.
OL,14,F"I'm not going to predict we are, but
OL,15,Fwe're aiming to win, absolutely. It's
OL,16,Fnow a fight (over) who comes first in
OL,17,Fthese elections.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
