OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776694271
OL,3,CFarage appears to row back on re-
OL,4,Copening Port Talbot's blast furnaces
OL,6,F"And it's a fight between us and Plaid
OL,7,Fas Labour, despite their enormous
OL,8,Fhistory here going back over a
OL,9,Fcentury, are not even in contention.
OL,11,F"Are we going to win? Well, you know
OL,12,Fwhat, we're going to try to."
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru and Reform have topped
OL,15,Frecent opinion polls in Wales, with
OL,16,FWelsh Labour forecast to lose its grip
OL,17,Fon the Senedd after more than two
OL,18,Fdecades.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@]O]
