OL,3,CFarage appears to row back on re-
OL,4,Copening Port Talbot's blast furnaces
OL,6,FDoreen Murray, 83, said: "(Labour)
OL,7,Fhave had enough time to prove
OL,8,Fthemselves.
OL,10,F"We need somebody with a bit of fight
OL,11,Fin them."
